Officially, the Social Welfare Agency is a government sponsored corporation that&#039;s inthe business of saving lives. At least, that&#039;s the ruse. In reality, it&#039;s and agency on the fringe of technology. They give terminal patients another shot at life uusing cybernetic implants. This conditioning process then shapes the patient into an efficient machine for handling all of the government&#039;s dirty work. 

They&#039; ve been given a second chance at life, but at what cost?

Set in scenic Italy, Gunslinger Girl uses beauty to offset the story&#039;s tragedy. Amidst awe-inspiring animaion and a superbly scored soundtrack, you will fall in love with five young girls whose fate has been sealed.
